	<key>readme</key>
	<string>AI Gateway — Multi-model routing through LiteLLM on your homelab.

Keywords:
  gw {query}      - Auto-route query (picks best model via gateway)
  code {query}    - Coding help (Claude Sonnet → GPT-5 → local)
  analyze {query} - Deep analysis (Claude Opus → Gemini Pro → local)
  ask {query}     - Quick chat (GPT-5 mini → Gemini Flash → local)
  sum             - Summarize clipboard contents
  rewrite {style} - Rewrite clipboard (formal, casual, concise, expand, fix-grammar)

Gateway: http://192.168.1.52:4000 (LiteLLM on Host C LXC 102)

Setup:
  LITELLM_MASTER_KEY - Your LiteLLM gateway API key (or leave blank for open LAN access)
  Key is auto-extracted from ~/.zshrc if not set as workflow variable.</string>
